data.description: Experience the epitome of affordable Florida living in this delightful first-floor corner unit located in the vibrant Twin Lakes community. This open-concept 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo is a haven of comfort and convenience. The glass enclosed patio allows for year round enjoyment of the tranquil surroundings. Washer/dryer hookup inside unit. Building is 55+ and is part of an active community that helps to enjoy all of the amenities this association has to offer! Close to shopping, restaurants, beaches and easy access to I-95!
